{"tha-ap327:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap327:0.2":"Umapupphiyavagga ","tha-ap327:0.3":"Nimittasannakattheraapadana ","tha-ap327:1.1":"“Candabhaganaditire, ","tha-ap327:1.2":"vasami assame aham; ","tha-ap327:1.3":"Suvannamigamaddakkhim, ","tha-ap327:1.4":"carantam vipine aham. ","tha-ap327:2.1":"Mige cittam pasadetva, ","tha-ap327:2.2":"lokajettham anussarim; ","tha-ap327:2.3":"Tena cittappasadena, ","tha-ap327:2.4":"anne buddhe anussarim. ","tha-ap327:3.1":"Abbhatita ca ye buddha, ","tha-ap327:3.2":"vattamana anagata; ","tha-ap327:3.3":"Evamevam virocanti, ","tha-ap327:3.4":"migarajava te tayo. ","tha-ap327:4.1":"Catunnavutito kappe, ","tha-ap327:4.2":"yam sannamalabhim tada; ","tha-ap327:4.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap327:4.4":"buddhasannayidam phalam. ","tha-ap327:5.1":"Sattavise ito kappe, ","tha-ap327:5.2":"eko asim mahipati; ","tha-ap327:5.3":"Arannasattho namena, ","tha-ap327:5.4":"cakkavatti mahabbalo. ","tha-ap327:6.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap327:6.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap327:6.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap327:7.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma nimittasannako thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap327:8.1":"Nimittasannakattherassapadanam pancamam. "}